They circulate numerous versions of the program, some even set a number of risks, so the insurance company in addition to the administration has only one thing to do, although there are small difficulties.
Among the disadvantages of the program is that some medications are multi-use drugs, for example certain substances serve to treat both headache and heat waves and even antidepressants.
